statements: SELECT * FROM charging_patterns;
SELECT vehicle_id, start_time, energy_consumed FROM charging_patterns WHERE grid_impact_rating > 5;
SELECT charging_id, end_time FROM charging_patterns WHERE energy_consumed < 50;
SELECT vehicle_id, start_time, end_time FROM charging_patterns ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT grid_impact_rating FROM charging_patterns;
SELECT * FROM charging_patterns WHERE energy_consumed > 50 ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT vehicle_id, SUM(energy_consumed) AS total_energy FROM charging_patterns GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING total_energy > 100 ORDER BY total_energy DESC;
SELECT * FROM charging_patterns WHERE grid_impact_rating = 3 AND start_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT vehicle_id, AVG(energy_consumed) AS avg_energy FROM charging_patterns GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING avg_energy < 30 ORDER BY avg_energy;
SELECT vehicle_id, COUNT(charging_id) AS charging_count FROM charging_patterns GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING charging_count >= 3 ORDER BY charging_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM electric_vehicle_charging
SELECT vehicle_id, charging_start, charging_end FROM electric_vehicle_charging
SELECT vehicle_id, charging_energy_kWh FROM electric_vehicle_charging WHERE charging_energy_kWh > 10
SELECT * FROM electric_vehicle_charging ORDER BY charging_start DESC
SELECT event_timestamp, event_description FROM grid_impact
SELECT * FROM electric_vehicle_charging WHERE charging_energy_kWh > 50 ORDER BY charging_start DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, charging_start, charging_end, charging_energy_kWh FROM electric_vehicle_charging WHERE vehicle_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM grid_impact WHERE impact_level = 'High' AND event_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY event_timestamp ASC;
SELECT vehicle_id, charging_start, charging_end, charging_energy_kWh FROM electric_vehicle_charging WHERE charging_start BETWEEN '2021-10-01' AND '2022-02-28';
SELECT * FROM grid_impact WHERE event_description LIKE '%outage%' ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM electric_vehicle;
SELECT id, vehicle_id, charging_status, charging_power FROM electric_vehicle WHERE charging_status = TRUE;
SELECT id, station_id, location FROM charging_station ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT * FROM charging_history WHERE vehicle_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT id, vehicle_id, start_time, end_time FROM charging_history WHERE end_time IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM electric_vehicle WHERE charging_status = TRUE;
SELECT vehicle_id, MIN(charging_power) FROM electric_vehicle GROUP BY vehicle_id ORDER BY MIN(charging_power) DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM charging_station WHERE location LIKE '%California%';
SELECT vehicle_id, COUNT(*) FROM charging_history WHERE end_time IS NOT NULL GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING COUNT(*) >= 5;
SELECT * FROM charging_station JOIN electric_vehicle ON charging_station.station_id = electric_vehicle.vehicle_id;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_name, city FROM charging_stations ORDER BY city DESC;
SELECT station_name, capacity FROM charging_stations WHERE capacity > 50;
SELECT vehicle_id, manufacturer, model FROM vehicles WHERE vehicle_type = 'Electric';
SELECT * FROM grid_impact WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2021-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2021-12-31 23:59:59';
SELECT * FROM charging_stations WHERE city='San Francisco';
SELECT station_name, city FROM charging_stations ORDER BY capacity DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, start_time, end_time FROM charging_sessions WHERE energy_usage > 50 ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT manufacturer, model FROM vehicles WHERE vehicle_type='Electric' AND manufacturer='Tesla';
SELECT * FROM grid_impact WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp < '2022-02-01';
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_id, location, capacity FROM charging_stations ORDER BY station_id DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, model, manufacturer FROM vehicles WHERE owner_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM charging_sessions WHERE start_time > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT station_id, impact_level, timestamp FROM grid_impact ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT * FROM charging_stations;
SELECT station_id, location, capacity FROM charging_stations WHERE location = 'New York';

SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, location, model FROM charging_sessions INNER JOIN vehicles ON charging_sessions.vehicle_id = vehicles.vehicle_id INNER JOIN charging_stations ON charging_sessions.station_id = charging_stations.station_id;
SELECT owner_id, name, email FROM owners WHERE owner_id IN (SELECT owner_id FROM vehicles WHERE manufacturer = 'Tesla');
SELECT station_id, impact_level, timestamp FROM grid_impact WHERE impact_level = 'High' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
